      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW PALMER (4) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 2 lengths at Horsham in a handy 23.00 beating Riversdale Mick. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. FLYING ROGUE (1) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from four tries. Below best last time at The Meadows (30.63) in a Grade 5 H, finishing a 7 length sixth. Can feature with the right run. MEPUNGA SHADOW (8) turned in a plain run last time when seventh at The Meadows over 525m behind Paw Gordy (30.75) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Can do much better this time. FEAR THE BEER (5) is new here but should be in the mix.",
